nodes.text: The Phelleem sector was a sector located in the Outer Rim Territories, rimward of Corva sector. Planets in Phelleem included Kashi and Naldar.
After the Battle of Endor, the Dark Lady of the Sith Lumiya tasked Dark Jedi Flint to conquer the entire Phelleem sector while she prepared the Nagai invasion of the galaxy.
